---
title: Sesame Salmon Rice Bowls with Mushrooms and Sriracha Mayo
description: Inspired by traditional gohan, Japanese stirred rice, this dish pairs flaky, sesame-crusted salmon with heaps of delicious veggies and a fragrant, savoury ginger-soy sauce – all mixed together in one delicious bowl. A little spicy mayo on top adds a bright, creamy zing!
